# <%= current_page.data.title %>

DSK International is easily accessible by car or train (Rokko Liner, Island Center Station), approximately 20 minutes from Sannomiya (Kobe's down-town area) and 35 minutes from Umeda (Osaka's down-town area).

## Enrolment Enquiries

Please email <%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto, data.config.contact.mailto %> or call **+81 <a href="tel:078 857 9777">(0)78-857-9777</a>** to speak to one of our office staff about enrolments.

Please visit our <%= link_to 'Admissions', local_path('admissions') %> section of the website for further details.

## School Tours

DSK International offers guided School tours providing an insight into the school on a normal school day.
Bookings are required for a school tour and we kindly ask you make your booking below:

<%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto + '?subject=School Tour', 'Book a tour »', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info', role: 'button' %>

## Open Events

Our Open Events provide a fun and unique opportunity to spend time with current students, parents, teachers and staff. We have a variety of open events happening at our school and attendance is free and bookings usually aren't required. Please see a list of our <%= link_to 'events here', local_path('news') %>.

## Open Days

Our school has two open days every year: one in March and one in November. This is one of the best opportunities to come and explore our school, meet the staff and get a sense for what life is like at DSKI. Details of the next open day will be available on the <%= link_to 'events page', local_path('news') %> very soon. If you are interested in booking your place at the open day please contact us here:

<%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto + '?Subject=Open Day', 'Open Day Enquiry »', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info', role: 'button' %>

